Build a world-class luxury fashion e-commerce platform called **CASA MILAN**. This is not just an online store—it is a premium digital fashion house that should feel comparable to luxury brands such as Louis Vuitton, Dior, Jacquemus, Aime Leon Dore, Fear of God, Zara Studio, and COS. Every page should feel elegant, refined, modern, editorial, and highly polished while maintaining exceptional speed and usability.

The entire project must be production-ready, scalable, secure, maintainable, and written using clean, modular code with enterprise-level architecture.

